          <tr class="border-b border-stone-100">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">工作强度</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">FAANG约50-60小时/周，有明确边界</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">字节/拼多多约70-90小时/周，大厂普遍偏高</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-stone-100">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">技术背景要求</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">多元——MBA、文科、CS背景都有成功PM</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">偏好理工背景，很多大厂PM要求CS/工程本科</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-stone-100">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">产品节奏</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">迭代节奏相对慢，更重用户研究和测试</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">极快迭代，先上线再优化，"快"是核心竞争力</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-stone-100">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">数据文化</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">数据驱动决策，A/B测试成本低，文化成熟</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">数据文化强，但更多老板拍板，数据有时是支持已有决策的工具</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">出路</td>
